name: Curve oETH Pool
description: This token represents a curve liquidity pool. Holders earn fees from users trading in the pool, and can also deposit the LP to Curve's gauges to earn CRV emissions. This curve pool contains ETH and OETH. OETH is Origin Protocol's liquid staking derivative for Ethereum, it is backed 1:1 by Ether along with liquid staking tokens stETH, rETH, and sfrxETH.
